    dct:title "Camtree Digital Library :: Home" @en ;
    dct:description "Repository and exchange platform dedicated to teacher-practitioner research and inquiry. Enables classroom-based teachers to share evidence from their own research to improve educational practice. Unique focus on practitioner-led educational knowledge creation and dissemination." @en ;
